Mireille Mary Wenger (amụrụ n'afọ 1980 ma ọ bụ n'afọ 1981) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa bụ onye bụ Minista na-ahụ maka ego na ohere akụ na ụba na Western Cape Provincial kemgbe Mee 2022 na onye otu Democratic Alliance (DA) onye otu Western Cape Províncial Parliament kemgbe Mee 2014
Ọ bụ Chief Whip nke Majority Party site na Mee 2019 ruo Mee 2022.

Wenger nwere Master of Arts na International Studies site na Mahadum Stellenbosch na Master of Philosophy (MPhil) na Criminology, Law and Society site na Machị Cape Town. O nwetara diplọma na sayensị ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na Sociology site na Sciences Po na France.
N'afọ 2014, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu Western Cape Provincial dị ka onye otu Democratic Alliance
Ọ malitere ọrụ dị ka MPP na 21 Mee 2014
A họpụtara Wenger ka ọ bụrụ onyeisi oche nke kọmitii nchekwa obodo.
Mgbe a họpụtara ya ọzọ na 2019, a họpụtara ọ ka ọ bụrụ onye isi ụtarị nke DA caucus ma si otú a bụrụ onye isi nke Majority Party
Ọ malitere ọrụ na 22 Mee 2019. N'abalị iri na asaa n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2022, a họpụtara Wenger dị ka onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Ad-Hoc nke Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Provincial na COVID-19.

N'abalị iri abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2022, onye isi ala Alan Winde kwupụtara na Wenger ga-esonye na kansụl mpaghara n'ụbọchị iri na isii n'ọnwarị afọ 2022 dị ka Minista na-ahụ maka ego na ohere akụ na ụba dị ka Minisita na-ahụ anya David Maynier ga-aga n'ọkwa agụmakwụkwọ iji dochie Debbie Schäfer, onye kwupụtara ọpụpụ ya na gọọmentị mpaghara. Kọmitii Ad-Hoc nke Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Provincial na COVID-19 gbasara na 10 Mee 2022. Onye otu DA Lorraine Botha nọchiri Wenger dị ka Chief Whip nke Majority Party. A ṅụrụ Wenger iyi n'ọkwa n'ụbọchị iri na isii nke ọnwa Mee afọ 2022.
